---
// Displayed prominently before The Experience, per the content brief.
---
<aside class="cw" role="note" aria-label="Cultural advice">
  <div class="container cw__inner">
    <p class="record cw__label">Aboriginal &amp; Torres Strait Islander peoples</p>
    <p class="cw__body">
      This experience contains the voices, images and stories of people who have passed away. We acknowledge
      the Traditional Custodians of the land on which this story is shared, and pay our respects to Elders past
      and present.
    </p>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .cw { border-block: 1px solid var(--line); background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25); }
  .cw__inner { padding: clamp(28px, 5vw, 48px) 0; max-width: 70ch; }
  .cw__label { color: var(--gold); margin: 0 0 12px; }
  .cw__body { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--bone-dim); margin: 0; font-style: italic; }
</style>
